JD - 8 : 

Key Responsibilities:
- Lead a team of Operations Leads to ensure customer delight and alignment with committed timelines
- Coordinate with design and production teams, as well as internal stakeholders for customer support
- Own the customer experience post-booking till project handover
- Act as the highest point of escalation for your region and ensure timely issue resolution
- Coordinate with cross-functional teams for faster issue resolution and empower team members
- Manage people, hiring, and ensure adherence to defined processes and standards
- Responsible for Customer Move In Timeline Adherence, Customer Overall CSAT Score, and quicker resolution of customer escalations

Qualifications Required:
- Preferably NIT/BITS/IIT/MBA from IIM/Tier 1 B-schools
- 7 to 10 years of work experience in Startups or Operations in similar industries
- Strong people management skills with direct team reporting experience
- Attention to detail, excellent communication skills, structured thought process, and analytical ability
- Ability to thrive in a fast-paced startup environment
- Experience in managing strategic alliances and business partnerships

